Streaming live on Twitch! https://www.twitch.tv/dougdoug
Follow me on twitter! https://twitter.com/DougDougFood

If you're curious how I set this up, I used the console command "tcl" to toggle collision, basically meaning that no creature or objects can move. Then I spawned all the creatures in the arena using player.placeatme command, and then once I want to start the fight I just say "tcl" again to trigger collision. Nothing super crazy but it's an easy way to set up custom fights

Title: DougDoug Channel Update! New videos and a new name
Description:
Content! Doug! 
Basically I've been trying out different concepts for videos and testing out weird ideas over the past months, and I want to start uploading them to this channel and actually getting peoples' thoughts on it

As a warning, these new videos are NOT very great in my opinion, but I'm at a point where I want to just heavily experiment with different concepts and see what works well - so if you have thoughts or criticism over the next few weeks as I put these out, I'll genuinely read and think about them since I want to keep improving

Logo artwork by my super talented friend Tyler Hooper: https://www.instagram.com/tylerhooper/

Thanks for checking it out, luv ya
